Begin regularSarethiGuard

;script on Sarethi guards to remove them during HR_GuardSarethi quest

if ( CellChanged == 0 )
	Return
endif

if ( GetJournalIndex HR_GuardSarethi > 0 )
	if ( GetJournalIndex HR_GuardSarethi < 100 )
		if ( GetDisabled == 0 )
			Disable
			Return
		endif
	endif
endif

if ( GetDisabled == 1 )
	Enable
endif

End
